videos.description: North Carolina's Joel Berry II gets the steal and Justin Jackson finishes with the layup.
videos.headline: UNC steal leads to Jackson's score

videos.description: North Carolina's Isaiah Hicks saves the ball from going out of bounds and Nate Britt uses a cross-over to then pass it to Tony Bradley for the two-handed dunk.
videos.headline: UNC's great passing leads to a Bradley dunk

videos.description: North Carolina's Kennedy Meeks makes the huge stuff against Notre Dame's Martinas Geban.
videos.headline: Meeks comes up strong with the block

videos.description: North Carolina's Justin Jackson hits a deep 3-pointer to spark the Tar Heels' offense in the second half.
videos.headline: Jackson hits deep 3 to spark UNC early in second half

videos.description: North Carolina's Justin Jackson finishes with the reverse layup.
videos.headline: Jackson gets acrobatic with layup

videos.description: North Carolina's Joel Berry II gets blocked on his 3-pointer attempt, but Isaiah Hicks is able to finish with the layup.
videos.headline: UNC converts off blocked 3

videos.description: Notre Dame's Steve Vasturia blocks North Carolina's Brandon Robinson.
videos.headline: Notre Dame stifles Tar Heels in the paint

videos.description: North Carolina's Roy Williams gets frustrated with the foul call on Isaiah Hicks.
videos.headline: Williams gets heated on the sideline after foul call on Hicks

videos.description: North Carolina's Nate Britt gets the steal and finds Justin Jackson who hammers home a two-handed dunk.
videos.headline: UNC's transition leads to clutch dunk

videos.description: North Carolina's coach Roy Williams discusses feelings down the stretch against No. 20 Notre Dame.
videos.headline: Roy Williams talks about thoughts during final moments against Notre Dame
